        <h1>Football:World's Popular Sport</h1>
        <h2>About it:</h2>
        <p>Football is known to be the worldâ€™s most popular game.<br> It is not only played between two different nations from around
        the world but also in our localities. It is also one of the most loved  games.<br> One speciality about the game is the
        enthusiasm of the players and viewers and the element of suspense that keeps everyone on the edge of their seats till
        the end of the game.</p>
        <hr>
        <h3>Play of the game</h3>
        <p>The rules of football regarding equipment, field of play, conduct of participants, and settling of results are built around 17 laws.<br>
             The International Football Association Board,consisting of delegates from FIFA and the four football associations from the United Kingdom,
              is empowered to amend the laws.</p>
